This package contains advanced versions of the predicate functional interfaces defined in the JDK package java.util.function.

Package de.boereck.matcher.function.predicate Description

This package contains advanced versions of the predicate functional interfaces defined in the JDK package java.util.function. The advanced versions include e.g. more boolean combinators for predicate results.
